issue.title: [Enhancement] Look back into nx-cloud integration for builds
issue.body:
**Describe the solution you'd like**
during PRs it appears, but idk how to integrate it into the current build. Or if that is even possible.

see:
https://nx.dev/nx-cloud/set-up/github


https://nx.dev/core-features/share-your-cache

comment.body:
current blocker seems to be the package of `@nrwl/nx-cloud` is stuck on version `15.0.2`, while the rest of nx is on `15.0.12` and the pipeline throws an error if these don't match.

Will continue to hold off until a new version drops.
